Class Title

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.destroystokyo.paper.Title
  • @Deprecated
public final class Title
extends java.lang.Object
    Deprecated.
    use Title
    Represents a title to may be sent to a Player.

    A title can be sent without subtitle text.
